PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT DISTINCT RXCOMMUNITY.NAME, RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID FROM RXCOMMUNITY RXCOMMUNITY, PSX_ROLES PSX_ROLES, RXCOMMUNITYROLE RXCOMMUNITYROLE WHERE PSX_ROLES.ID = RXCOMMUNITYROLE.ROLEID AND RXCOMMUNITYROLE.COMMUNITYID = RXCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID AND PSX_ROLES.NAME IN (:"PSXSingleParam/sys_userrolenames") ORDER BY RXCOMMUNITY.NAME ASC

SELECT REVISIONID, MAX(ACTOR) AS ACTOR, MAX(EVENTTIME) AS EVENTTIME, MAX(TRANSITIONCOMMENT) AS TRANSITIONCOMMENT FROM CONTENTSTATUSHISTORY WHERE CONTENTID = :PSXParam/sys_contentid GROUP BY REVISIONID
